parameters:
(It feels really unpleasant... But if a girl is
asking for help, I have to search...)\F[4]
"If I cut the rope like this"\n<Yukine>\F[1]
(It's calling me. It must be this mansion...)\F[10]
"If I cut the rope like this"\n<Yukine>\F[1]
"I'm home. Sorry to keep you waiting. Sorry, Mom."\n<Frog>
(There's something lying where the frog was.)

"You've always... had regrets, haven't you? Were
you able to... go to your mother's place?"\n<Yukine>\F[6]

(This well... it's old, but it seems there's water
collected at the bottom.)

(As I peered in, part of the well crumbled, and
before I knew it, my body was being sucked into
the well--)

(With a terribly dull sound echoing in the back of
my head, everything went pitch black.)

(With this depth, I can't draw water with a
bucket...)

(With this, I should be able to draw water from
the well.)

"Haah, that was heavy. Now I need to find a
container for the water..."\n<Yukine>\F[12]

(This well... it's old, but it seems there's water
collected at the bottom.)
(But there's no "bucket" to draw the water.)
(I need to find a container for water.)
"I've obtained a dish filled with water."
"(I should give this to the bird to drink.)"
(Is there anything else that might be useful?)
(Just here, the soil is slightly raised.)

(This... it's a hairpin. Could this be... a gift,
I wonder. There's also a pair of scissors buried
with it.)\F[5]

(Red berries are growing. This is... fruit, isn't
it?)

(Is this the strawberry that Kaeru-san was talking
about... I wonder?)
(I should tell Mr. Frog about this.)
